{"tid":616023,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"深V晃奶！「魔鬼胸」狂露東西半球　一轉身…全裸美背見客","createTime":"2018-04-03T23:55:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T11:27:12.000Z","uid":81228,"like":5,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"542f17aaaed9c52ba83078fdcfc9749faf23149a","tid":616023,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T23:55:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/04/02/1306783-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F1306783-XXL.jpg&h=e0224aa4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲蔚雨芯因傲人身材擁有「魔鬼胸」稱號。（圖／翻攝自蔚雨芯IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/04/02/1306781-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F1306781-XXL.jpg&h=0c19d43b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼蔚雨芯愚人節大方放送好身材。（圖／翻攝自蔚雨芯IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/04/02/1306782-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F1306782-XXL.jpg&h=7b8706cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/04/02/1306787-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F1306787-XXL.jpg&h=e32471db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲蔚雨芯去年赴陸發展受到吳奇隆賞識。（圖／翻攝自蔚雨芯IG）<br />\n<br />\n24歲港星蔚雨芯長相艷麗，因32D傲人身材擁有「魔鬼胸」稱號，出道後迅速走紅，人氣超高。昨（1）日適逢愚人節，她也開心透過IG放送性感美照，只見她對著鏡頭撥弄一頭浪漫捲髮，胸前深V東西半球全見客，令人噴鼻血的是，蔚雨芯一轉身，竟裸曬白皙美背，辣照掀起網友暴動。<br />\n<br />\n蔚雨芯昨在IG的限時動態中上傳一段影片，畫面中她身穿黑色深V上衣，露出東西半球，深邃事業線一覽無遺，隨後她也發文祝大家愚人節快樂，並曝光該件上衣的最大亮點，照片中她背部全裸，僅用兩根黑繩交叉撐起整件上衣，窈窕身材令人驚艷，性感模樣曝光後，立刻吸引大批粉絲激動直呼「好正啊啊啊啊啊啊啊」、「背影真美」、「美女中的美人兒」、「性感」。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，蔚雨芯因13歲參加比賽表演唱歌而發掘，2012年出道後還被譽為「翻版周秀娜」及「翻版樂基兒」，因身材關係受到矚目，她曾揚言要擺脫「魔鬼胸」稱號以實力取代身材，去年一度消失香港娛樂圈，後傳出是前往大陸發展，更被吳奇隆看中，簽下她做旗下音樂公司的歌手兼演員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=364510\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D364510&d=fMMf8xppSEyiJECW3yj3UqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=22fdd4ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D364510&h=adbc3db0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=364510</a>"},{"pid":"edcfbd3f1f728a288ac39249be1fccbea6dcfd54","tid":616023,"uid":82450,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T00:03:50.000Z","msg":"比人叫翻板樂基兒好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35343d656193b3a929cc9f859d28807ae7911d13","tid":616023,"uid":160916,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T00:05:48.000Z","msg":"人氣超高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b064514df313a0833e39293a61ec77c4a3d7072","tid":616023,"uid":18587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T00:10:41.000Z","msg":"32D即係大定唔大？"},{"pid":"7b716b9240cef941ea3c35fd3c5eaa090323c01a","tid":616023,"uid":117894,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T00:19:19.000Z","msg":"呢個我真係j唔落"},{"pid":"d662a53a1794c3657b309b6f728c529146096663","tid":616023,"uid":32721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T00:20:41.000Z","msg":"俾大陸老細潛左未？"},{"pid":"7fd921fdbe89c9fb121c0594b32ea43bf0044c10","tid":616023,"uid":73596,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T00:20:53.000Z","msg":"雞味濃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25ef6ecfc96f3374d278375a807dd2bf0f30840a","tid":616023,"uid":37612,"like":4,"dislike":14,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T00:26:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/04/082559_c0dba9f8998014cebab9e625aa64e83b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F04%2F082559_c0dba9f8998014cebab9e625aa64e83b.png&h=6bcbebb3&s={SIZE}\